sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant View as Wilayah Form
    participant Controller as WilayahController
    participant ModelW as Wilayah Model
    participant ModelA as Admin Model
    participant DB as Database
    
    Admin->>View: Input Data Wilayah & Admin Baru
    View->>Controller: POST /admin/wilayah
    
    Note right of Controller: Start Database Transaction
    
    Controller->>ModelW: Create Wilayah
    ModelW->>DB: Insert Wilayah
    DB-->>ModelW: Return ID
    
    Controller->>ModelA: Create Admin User (Role: admin_wilayah)
    ModelA->>DB: Insert Admin
    DB-->>ModelA: Success
    
    alt Transaction Success
        Controller->>DB: Commit
        Controller-->>View: Redirect Success
    else Error
        Controller->>DB: Rollback
        Controller-->>View: Show Error
    end
    
    opt Filter by Role (Admin Wilayah)
        Admin->>View: View Index
        View->>Controller: GET /index
        Controller->>Controller: Check Username Pattern (provinsi-...)
        Controller->>ModelW: Filter parent_id based on Province Match
        ModelW-->>Controller: Return Filtered Data
    end
